      "writtenOn": "2019-11-13T03:38:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The problem I am trying to solve is stopping work after the context is cancelled, but it\u0027s hard to do cleanly since none of the functions for reading on a connection or parsing JSON accept a context.\n\nIs there a common pattern for creating a context-sensitive wrapper for a context-insensitive blocking operation?",
      "parentUuid": "481d6a5a_b298cdcd",
      "revId": "4118cc1cfbb7163bb259e7e37720f66cdd1c231d",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "ffb949d5_5bcbf395",
        "filename": "resultdb/sink/sink.go",
        "patchSetId": 15
      },
      "lineNbr": 220,
      "author": {
        "id": 1114299
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-11-13T16:33:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "typically either a function either accepts a context or guarantees to return shortly.\nlooks like processMessages should accept ctx and check ctx.Err() in the beginning of the loop. Then we don\u0027t need this additional goroutine",
      "parentUuid": "6fcfe1ad_96e5e7d9",
      "revId": "4118cc1cfbb7163bb259e7e37720f66cdd1c231d",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "7ede6e50_6addcd0f",
        "filename": "resultdb/sink/sink.go",
        "patchSetId": 15
      },
      "lineNbr": 220,
      "author": {
        "id": 1333728
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-11-14T02:13:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Tried to do this, and it turns out my code hangs if the client does not send any data, since readMessage will just wait forever. This can be fixed by setting deadlines on the connection object itself, but that requires exposing the fact that it is a connection all the way down at readMessage, when I would rather that function just accept a json.Decoder. I think it would be better to keep the goroutine but make sure that it will always be terminated.",
      "parentUuid": "ffb949d5_5bcbf395",
      "revId": "4118cc1cfbb7163bb259e7e37720f66cdd1c231d",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
